                "**Rules**\n\n- Be civil, don't attack or insult others. Offending posts/comments may be removed and users banned. [Code of Conduct](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/code_of_conduct.html)\n- Do not ask for invites to trackers or indexers, there are other places for this purpose.\n- Stay on topic, posts unrelated to Radarr will be removed.\n- Don't provide/request access/links for series, movies, or other content you don't have the rights to.\n- No Trolling or Baiting.\n- No Ads / Spamming.",
